1.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">- We will only retain personal information as long as necessary for the fulfillment of those purposes. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 5.0px 18.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">- We will collect personal information by lawful and fair means and, where appropriate, with the knowledge or consent of the individual concerned. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 5.0px 18.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">- Personal data should be relevant to the purposes for which it is to be used, and, to the extent necessary for those purposes, should be accurate, complete, and up-to-date. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 5.0px 18.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">- We will protect personal information by reasonable security safeguards against loss or theft, as well as unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, use or modification. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 18.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">- We will make readily available to customers information about our policies and practices relating to the management of personal information. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 2.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">We are committed to conducting our business in accordance with these principles in order to ensure that the confidentiality of personal information is protected and maintained. </span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 9.0px Verdana; color: #424242; min-height: 11.0px;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;"><strong>Refund Policy</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Verdana; color: #424242; min-height: 15.0px;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 5.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;"><strong>Annual Membership Refund Policy</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Annual Memberships may be refunded at a prorated amount, based on the number of months that have elapsed since the membership was purchased, and calculated at the monthly membership rate of 1/12</span><span style="font: 7.3px Verdana; letter-spacing: 0.0px;"><sup>th</sup></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;"> of an annual premium.  No refunds will be given on expired annual memberships.  Refund request may be submitted at any time via the customer service link.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Verdana; color: #424242; min-height: 15.0px;"> </p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 5.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;"><strong>Monthly Membership Auto-Draft Cancellation</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Verdana; color: #424242;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Auto-Draft payments are non refundable.  In order to cancel Monthly Auto-Draft, the main account holder must submit a completed Auto-Draft Cancellation Form via the customer service link.</span></p>', 1, 1);
